- File names should start with small capital letters e.g button
- Function name should be with capital letters of the file name e.g if file name is "button" function name will be "Button".
- Work with atomic structure.
- Always export a default function.
- Appropriate variable names.
- Appropriate Branch names with capital letters.
- To run project use npm run dev.
- To run prisma use npx prisma studio (MAKE SURE TO BE IN THE RIGHT DIR).
- To update prisma schema do the following :
  1. npx prisma migrate dev --name (a name)
  2. reset all date ? yes
  3. 